public abstract class FValueInputBase
extends com.fluidops.ajax.components.FHorizontalLayouter
implements com.fluidops.ajax.components.groupeddataview.EditFieldComponent, ValueInput

Provides a set of common basic routines for RDF value input components implementing EditFieldComponent, such as initialization and validation methods. The component renders as a simple FHorizontalLayouter, which arranges any actual component(s).

In particular: (a) the class initializes the component with an RDF value, stored in protected variable , (b) implements required callback setter methods from EditFieldComponent and stores the callbacks in protected variables and (c) provides protected validation methods.

Author:
cp
